## ğŸš€ Quick Start

### Desktop Piano (Piano-CPP)

```bash
# Extract
unzip piano-cpp.zip
cd piano-cpp

# Build (Linux/Mac)
./build.sh

# Build (Windows)
build.bat

# Run
./piano
```

**Play:** Use QWERTY keys (Z-M, Q-U, I-P)
**Controls:** `[` `]` for octave, `-` `=` for velocity, `SPACE` for sustain

### Mobile Piano (Piano-Mobile)

```bash
# Install SDL2
sudo apt-get install libsdl2-dev libsdl2-ttf-dev

# Extract and build
unzip piano-mobile.zip
cd piano-mobile
make

# Run
./mobile-piano              # Default
./mobile-piano 1280 720     # HD resolution
```

**Play:** Click/touch piano keys
**Controls:** Top UI buttons for all features

